content.description:
This is a large lake / regional park where you can rent your own island to camp on. It has a few boulders but most notably Paroi de l’elephant (marker 63D on the Park’s map).
A couple campsites are in walking distance as well as an island campsite just across the water.

​https://poissonblanc.ca/en/​​​
